seller.description:
I am an on-camera actor and voice over actor. I have a wide range of accents and character voices that I can perform in both Spanish and English. Because of my background and training as an on camera actor I have been able to refine my voice over technique. I am able to take direction and deliver a product with few takes. 
I have done VO for Buick as well as other Spanish television spots and web and corporate training videos. I have appeared in television shows such as The Invisible Man, Eighteen Wheels of Justice, American Crime, From Dusk Till Dawn, Lonestar, Dallas, NCIS New Orleans.
